manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "actix-web-demo"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "actix-web-demo"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = []
keywords = []
categories = []
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = true

[dependencies]
actix-rt = "1"
actix-web = "3"
derive_more = "0.99.0"
dotenv = "0.15.0"
env_logger = "*"
jsonwebtoken = "8"
once_cell = "1.9.0"
serde = "1"
serde_json = "1"

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4"
features = ["serde"]
optional = false

[dependencies.sqlx]
version = "0.4.2"
features = ["runtime-actix-native-tls", "postgres", "chrono"]
optional = false
